1
00:00:02,961 --> 00:00:07,424
Pre moju lásku spravím čokoľvek.

2
00:00:07,799 --> 00:00:09,217
Vy nie?

3
00:00:10,385 --> 00:00:12,804
Áno, moje city.

4
00:00:17,809 --> 00:00:18,393
Shizuru!

5
00:00:21,855 --> 00:00:23,940
Dobre, urobím čo chceš.

6
00:00:24,482 --> 00:00:26,818
Ale predtým sa chcem stretnúť s Lordom Kokuyou.

7
00:01:59,703 --> 00:02:00,662
Mikoto?

8
00:02:02,455 --> 00:02:03,915
Zničím ju.

9
00:02:04,958 --> 00:02:06,292
Rozkázal to Ani-ue.

10
00:02:50,003 --> 00:02:52,839
Keby som mala na výber, tak by som ju nebudila.

11
00:02:57,385 --> 00:03:01,431
Tento systém obsahuje pamäť od poslednej
aktivácie.

12
00:03:02,182 --> 00:03:05,393
Chcete ju vymazať, a vytvoriť nového vlastníka?

13
00:03:06,269 --> 00:03:07,312
Pamäť?

14
00:03:27,290 --> 00:03:29,000
To ti nedovolím!

15
00:03:29,334 --> 00:03:31,378
Ona je naša jediná šanca.

16
00:03:34,506 --> 00:03:35,006
Miroku!

17
00:03:53,692 --> 00:03:54,401
Gakutenou!

18
00:04:10,375 --> 00:04:11,626
Choď sa pozrieť.

19
00:04:12,335 --> 00:04:13,920
Budem ťa sledovať.

20
00:04:14,295 --> 00:04:14,921
Mai HiME.

21
00:04:28,018 --> 00:04:28,643
Midori!

22
00:04:30,562 --> 00:04:31,146
Vydrž.

23
00:04:32,063 --> 00:04:32,397
Mai.

24
00:04:38,695 --> 00:04:39,904
Mikoto?

25
00:04:42,157 --> 00:04:42,490
Mai.

26
00:04:43,450 --> 00:04:44,242
Ty žiješ?

27
00:04:45,285 --> 00:04:47,287
Mai, dávaj si pozor.

28
00:04:52,167 --> 00:04:55,503
Ukáž mi teda, že to myslíš vážne.

29
00:04:57,630 --> 00:04:58,631
Takže toto si tým myslel.

30
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:03,219
To je tvoje Dieťa?

31
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:08,475
Je to moc, ktorú mi dal Ani-ue, Lord Kokuyou.

32
00:05:09,225 --> 00:05:09,893
Kokuyou...

33
00:05:15,231 --> 00:05:16,191
Gakutenou...

34
00:05:21,196 --> 00:05:23,740
Mikoto, nie! To je....

35
00:05:59,609 --> 00:06:00,985
Miyu?

36
00:06:08,451 --> 00:06:12,330
Prepáčte profesor, bol by ste hrdý nie?

37
00:06:16,334 --> 00:06:17,335
Midori!

38
00:06:27,929 --> 00:06:28,388
Mikoto!

39
00:06:30,140 --> 00:06:31,850
Som rada, že žiješ.

40
00:06:32,392 --> 00:06:34,185
Ale prečo to robíš?

41
00:06:35,145 --> 00:06:37,355
Kvôli Ani-ue.

42
00:06:38,106 --> 00:06:41,067
Mám rada len jeho.

43
00:06:42,485 --> 00:06:44,571
Milujem ho.

44
00:06:45,155 --> 00:06:48,158
To nieje pravá láska.

45
00:06:48,658 --> 00:06:50,869
Potom, aká je pravá?

46
00:06:53,288 --> 00:06:55,832
Potom, aká je pravá láska?

47
00:06:58,043 --> 00:06:59,753
Ani-ue povedal, že ma miluje.

48
00:07:00,670 --> 00:07:02,672
Vravel, že je so mnou šťastný.

49
00:07:06,217 --> 00:07:10,597
Preto teraz bojujem s ním.

50
00:07:12,724 --> 00:07:13,433
Mikoto!

51
00:07:18,188 --> 00:07:18,730
Fujino?

52
00:07:19,564 --> 00:07:21,149
Fujino, vy ste....

53
00:07:29,616 --> 00:07:30,617
Prestaň, Shizuru!

54
00:07:31,868 --> 00:07:32,202
Natsuki.

55
00:07:34,954 --> 00:07:36,956
Ty si nás počula?

56
00:07:39,292 --> 00:07:40,460
Natsu...ki

57
00:07:44,964 --> 00:07:45,382
Nie!!

58
00:07:49,177 --> 00:07:51,096
Nechcela som, aby si to vedela.

59
00:07:52,180 --> 00:07:55,767
Vedela som, že takto ma nebudeš milovať.

60
00:07:56,810 --> 00:07:57,811
Vedela som tiež....

61
00:08:06,361 --> 00:08:07,320
Kikukawa.

62
00:08:09,155 --> 00:08:12,367
Koniec je blízko, však?

63
00:08:13,743 --> 00:08:16,371
Musíme to ukončiť.

64
00:08:18,456 --> 00:08:20,333
Shizuru, prestaň!

65
00:08:28,508 --> 00:08:29,426
Čo to má celé znamenať?

66
00:08:30,051 --> 00:08:30,760
Haruka!

67
00:08:31,302 --> 00:08:35,306
Neverila by som, že si klesla tak hlboko.

68
00:08:35,807 --> 00:08:40,270
Pretože odhalila tvoje slabiny, ohrozuješ ju nožom?

69
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:44,065
Čo ste to za prezidentku študentskej rady?

70
00:08:44,232 --> 00:08:45,817
Haruka, neprovokuj ju.

71
00:08:46,234 --> 00:08:46,985
Ticho!

72
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:49,237
Čo sa deje, hádam sa len nebojíš?

73
00:08:49,362 --> 00:08:52,240
Potom zmizni, skôr ako spravíš podobnú úbohosť!

74
00:08:52,615 --> 00:08:54,701
Nedovolím, aby si Yukino skrivila vlas na hlave.

75
00:08:56,578 --> 00:08:59,789
Ustúp. Toto nieje nič pre teba.

76
00:09:00,957 --> 00:09:02,375
Do všetkého pcháš nos.

77
00:09:05,378 --> 00:09:06,087
Kiyohime.

78
00:09:19,309 --> 00:09:21,728
Shizuru, prestaň....Shizuru.

79
00:09:22,062 --> 00:09:22,771
Haruka.

80
00:09:24,939 --> 00:09:25,982
Čo teraz?

81
00:09:26,232 --> 00:09:27,525
Prosím, uteč!

82
00:09:28,318 --> 00:09:28,818
Duran!

83
00:09:29,235 --> 00:09:30,862
Prosím, príď, Duran!

84
00:09:31,738 --> 00:09:32,322
Duran!

85
00:09:33,031 --> 00:09:33,740
Natsuki!

86
00:09:35,658 --> 00:09:37,577
Ochránim ťa.

87
00:09:44,209 --> 00:09:44,626
Yukino.

88
00:09:45,126 --> 00:09:45,627
Diana!

89
00:10:16,324 --> 00:10:18,326
Nie....ty si....

90
00:10:22,622 --> 00:10:23,289
Haruka?

91
00:10:25,458 --> 00:10:26,960
Čo je to?

92
00:10:36,886 --> 00:10:37,595
Haruka!

93
00:10:37,846 --> 00:10:38,805
Ostaň kde si.

94
00:10:39,723 --> 00:10:43,560
Fujino, môžeš si myslieť, že si vyhrala,

95
00:10:44,853 --> 00:10:47,897
ale nanešťastie pre teba, ja som Suzushiro Haruka.

96
00:10:49,190 --> 00:10:50,567
Neprehrávam.

97
00:10:53,987 --> 00:10:57,157
Na mňa neplatia nejaké....

98
00:10:58,700 --> 00:10:59,868
posrané kúzla!

99
00:11:07,167 --> 00:11:07,667
Yukino!

100
00:11:09,794 --> 00:11:10,378
Haruka!

101
00:11:11,087 --> 00:11:11,629
Yukino.

102
00:11:14,883 --> 00:11:16,551
Si úžasná, Haruka.

103
00:11:19,137 --> 00:11:19,763
Ja....

104
00:11:32,901 --> 00:11:34,444
Haruka....

105
00:11:39,199 --> 00:11:40,450
Aké, zábavné.

106
00:11:42,077 --> 00:11:43,495
No nieje úbohá?

107
00:11:44,162 --> 00:11:47,290
Myslíš, že ju to zachráni?

108
00:11:50,043 --> 00:11:51,920
Už to netreba ďalej tajiť.

109
00:11:52,462 --> 00:11:53,254
Natsuki....

110
00:11:54,089 --> 00:11:57,425
milujem ťa.

111
00:11:57,759 --> 00:11:58,927
Shizu...ru...

112
00:11:59,678 --> 00:12:07,394
Porazím všetky ostatné HiME, a zničím všetko to, čo
nenávidíš.

113
00:12:08,978 --> 00:12:10,563
Vydrž, kvôli mne.

114
00:12:13,149 --> 00:12:14,484
Počkaj, Shizuru!

115
00:12:15,318 --> 00:12:16,111
Shizuru!

116
00:12:19,572 --> 00:12:20,990
Ohh, strašidelné.

117
00:12:21,324 --> 00:12:24,160
Je to tak, ako si predpokladal.

118
00:12:24,494 --> 00:12:28,957
Nagi, povedz jej, kde sú nepriatelia Natsuki.

119
00:12:29,624 --> 00:12:32,168
A tiež, prečo sa First District volá First District.

120
00:12:32,544 --> 00:12:33,670
Rozkaz, pane.

121
00:12:34,587 --> 00:12:37,590
Po 300 rokoch spánku som to pochopil.

122
00:12:38,174 --> 00:12:39,843
Tento svet končí.

123
00:12:40,969 --> 00:12:45,390
Ale pokým sú naokolo tie strigy, nikdy sa tento
cyklus neskončí.

124
00:12:46,349 --> 00:12:49,227
Budúcnosť musia vytvoriť mladí ľudia.

125
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:57,569
Takže, si Lord Kokuyou? Alebo Kaznzaki...
ehm, Minagi Reito?

126
00:13:12,083 --> 00:13:13,084
Drahá Mai,

127
00:13:14,502 --> 00:13:18,214
Sľúbila som ti, že si môžeš toto prečítať hneď,
ako to bude hotové.

128
00:13:19,382 --> 00:13:25,347
Nieje to ešte kompletné, ale chcem aby si vedela,
čo som zistila ohľadne boja HiME.

129
00:13:26,556 --> 00:13:30,352
Pamätáš sa na tú jaskyňu, kde stáli tie piliere?

130
00:13:31,436 --> 00:13:35,732
Keď osoba najbližšia HiME zomrie, vyrastie tam jeden pilier.

131
00:13:36,775 --> 00:13:43,907
Keď ich tam bude 11, a ostane už len posledná HiME,
otvorí sa hlavná brána.

132
00:13:44,991 --> 00:13:48,995
Tá HiME bude potom môcť vládnuť mocou hviezdy HiME.

133
00:13:49,871 --> 00:13:51,456
Ale je tu jedna podmineka.

134
00:13:52,791 --> 00:13:56,753
Musí sa vydať sa za Lorda Kokuyou.

135
00:13:59,130 --> 00:14:00,006
Hej, Mai.

136
00:14:01,049 --> 00:14:04,719
Neviem, kto je pre teba najdôležitejší,

137
00:14:05,428 --> 00:14:08,515
ale choď za hlasom svojho srdca.

138
00:14:10,016 --> 00:14:14,896
Pre nás znamená milovať niekoho, jeho ohrozenie.

139
00:14:15,730 --> 00:14:20,819
Ale kvôli tomu je naša láska
k tomu človeku ešte silnejšia.

140
00:14:23,822 --> 00:14:25,699
Prepáč, Midori.

141
00:14:26,908 --> 00:14:30,286
Ale ak je to preto, tak ma to nezaujíma.

142
00:14:31,329 --> 00:14:34,290
Potom, aká je pravá?

143
00:14:34,374 --> 00:14:36,835
Potom, aká je pravá láska?

144
00:14:37,210 --> 00:14:40,547
Čo je...

145
00:14:51,933 --> 00:14:55,437
Prečo sa toto stalo?

146
00:14:56,104 --> 00:14:59,315
Bolo tam niečo dôležité?

147
00:15:02,110 --> 00:15:02,527
Áno.

148
00:15:03,111 --> 00:15:05,071
Naozaj? Potom je to OK.

149
00:15:05,780 --> 00:15:08,450
Myslím, že raz by z nej mohla byť učiteľka.

150
00:15:11,578 --> 00:15:13,079
Sestra si to tu zabudla..

151
00:15:13,663 --> 00:15:17,417
Včera sa cítila vyčerpaná, tak tu odpočívala.

152
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:19,294
Aha.

153
00:15:20,128 --> 00:15:21,713
Chovala sa dosť náladovo.

154
00:15:22,255 --> 00:15:25,050
Musela tu byť prvý krát,

155
00:15:25,467 --> 00:15:30,055
a vyzeralo to, že nikdy nebola v nemocnici.

156
00:15:30,513 --> 00:15:31,389
Prvý krát?

157
00:15:31,765 --> 00:15:32,098
Áno.

158
00:15:34,059 --> 00:15:36,436
Ale mala zranenú ruku.

159
00:15:37,812 --> 00:15:42,984
To som si veru nevšimla, ale včera
vôbec nevyzerala byť zranená.

160
00:15:43,735 --> 00:15:44,611
Sestra!

161
00:15:47,572 --> 00:15:50,950
Zasratý fagan! Vraj posledná šanca.

162
00:15:51,159 --> 00:15:52,202
Nezahrávaj sa so mnou!

163
00:15:54,662 --> 00:15:55,372
Čo tak čumíš?

164
00:15:57,499 --> 00:15:58,792
Nedívaj sa na mňa tak.

165
00:15:59,417 --> 00:16:01,127
Ja som ten, čo ťa znesvätil.

166
00:16:01,544 --> 00:16:02,462
Nenáviď ma!

167
00:16:02,921 --> 00:16:05,632
Potrebujem, aby si pre mňa bojovala.

168
00:16:09,427 --> 00:16:10,845
Nemôžem v tom už pokračovať.

169
00:16:18,645 --> 00:16:20,897
Milujem ťa, Wataru.

170
00:16:28,863 --> 00:16:30,990
To už ozaj ideš?

171
00:16:31,157 --> 00:16:33,618
Hej, mám ešte prácu.

172
00:16:34,119 --> 00:16:40,125
Potom mi sľúb, že prídeš do parku pri nemocnici
o tretej.

173
00:16:41,626 --> 00:16:43,169
Prečo do parku?

174
00:16:43,545 --> 00:16:46,172
Takže si to aj tak nepamätáš.

175
00:16:48,133 --> 00:16:51,720
Dobre, aj tak už budem so všetkým hotový.

176
00:16:53,596 --> 00:16:56,349
Sľúbil si to. Nezabudni.

177
00:16:57,976 --> 00:16:59,686
Táto Shiho je teda....

178
00:17:06,609 --> 00:17:07,068
Kuga!

179
00:17:08,570 --> 00:17:14,034
Neboj sa, zničím všetko, čo nemáš rada.

180
00:17:14,284 --> 00:17:15,201
Prestaň, Shizuru.

181
00:17:16,244 --> 00:17:17,037
Už dosť!

182
00:17:21,291 --> 00:17:23,543
Počul som, že si omdlela priamo na ulici.

183
00:17:24,669 --> 00:17:25,920
Previezli ťa sem.

184
00:17:26,921 --> 00:17:30,550
Bude dobré, ak tu ostanem.

185
00:17:32,218 --> 00:17:33,845
S tebou sa tiež niečo deje.

186
00:17:35,096 --> 00:17:36,681
Si tiež HiME, však?

187
00:17:37,223 --> 00:17:38,224
Čo sa stalo?

188
00:17:38,534 --> 00:17:40,501
Je to to isté, ako s Tokihou.

189
00:17:40,727 --> 00:17:41,227
S Mai?

190
00:17:46,775 --> 00:17:49,069
Mám pre teba otázku.

191
00:17:54,824 --> 00:17:56,785
Aha, takže ona....

192
00:17:58,661 --> 00:18:00,747
Osud HiME ničí všetko naokolo.

193
00:18:02,207 --> 00:18:03,625
Máš rád Mai?

194
00:18:04,959 --> 00:18:06,044
Neviem.

195
00:18:06,628 --> 00:18:07,337
Ale.

196
00:18:09,130 --> 00:18:09,673
To...

197
00:18:10,632 --> 00:18:12,008
Čo do pekla?

198
00:18:13,593 --> 00:18:17,430
HiME bojuje o život toho, koho
má najradšej.

199
00:18:19,224 --> 00:18:24,938
Keď je HiME porazená, ten, koho má najradšej zomrie.

200
00:18:26,314 --> 00:18:27,315
Potom Takumi....

201
00:18:27,649 --> 00:18:31,069
Takumiho milovala iná HiME, ale bola porazená.

202
00:18:31,903 --> 00:18:37,450
Správne. Potom, Mai miluje niekoho iného.

203
00:18:38,827 --> 00:18:41,287
To som ja.

204
00:18:41,746 --> 00:18:42,414
Zbohom.

205
00:18:43,623 --> 00:18:45,500
Nevrav mi, že...

206
00:18:47,794 --> 00:18:48,211
Tate?

207
00:18:48,795 --> 00:18:49,671
Doriti!

208
00:19:00,265 --> 00:19:02,976
Doriti! Doriti! Doriti! Doriti!

209
00:19:03,560 --> 00:19:04,102
Mai!

210
00:19:06,062 --> 00:19:11,860
Boj začal hneď ako si ušla po útoku od Nao.

211
00:19:12,402 --> 00:19:14,070
To sa ti len zdalo.

212
00:19:14,571 --> 00:19:17,032
To bola moja dvojníčka.

213
00:19:17,490 --> 00:19:19,242
Takže ty za to môžeš.

214
00:19:22,203 --> 00:19:25,623
Ak ma porazíš, prijmem svoj osud.

215
00:19:26,082 --> 00:19:31,588
Ale nechcem, aby si zhrešila kvôli niekomu,
koho miluješ.

216
00:19:36,009 --> 00:19:37,052
O čom to hovoríš?

217
00:19:37,552 --> 00:19:39,846
To všetko kvôli tvojmu klamstvu.

218
00:19:41,556 --> 00:19:42,474
Klamstvu?
Myslím, že je to pravda.

219
00:19:43,767 --> 00:19:49,230
Plánuješ poraziť aj ostatné HiME, a vyhrať tento boj?

220
00:19:49,522 --> 00:19:52,609
Jasne, zvíťazím, a privediem Takumiho späť.

221
00:19:52,984 --> 00:19:53,985
A on bude...

222
00:19:56,321 --> 00:19:58,948
To je to, po čom ozaj túžiš?

223
00:20:00,492 --> 00:20:03,203
Čo naozaj chceš?

224
00:20:26,267 --> 00:20:27,477
Vitaj.

225
00:20:28,103 --> 00:20:29,813
Meškáš.

226
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:33,358
Celý čas som tu na teba čakala.

227
00:20:34,067 --> 00:20:34,484
Nao.

228
00:20:38,863 --> 00:20:44,577
Spomínaš si braček?
Dnes je výročie dňa, kedy sme sa pred rokmi stretli.

229
00:21:09,144 --> 00:21:11,521
Sľúbili sme...

230
00:21:12,188 --> 00:21:14,816
To zranenie ma stále bolí.

231
00:21:15,108 --> 00:21:17,193
Lezie mi to ozaj na na nervy.

232
00:21:17,944 --> 00:21:20,905
A neprestane, nech potrestám neviem koľko chlapov.

233
00:21:22,323 --> 00:21:25,910
Ale keď mám teba, možno hej.

234
00:21:29,622 --> 00:21:33,126
Mai, to, čo ľudia naozaj chcú....

235
00:21:33,293 --> 00:21:34,794
je vždy niekto iný.

236
00:21:38,631 --> 00:21:41,009
Musia sa rozhodnúť.

237
00:21:41,968 --> 00:21:45,764
Čo je najdôležitejšie pre každého z nich.

238
00:22:00,195 --> 00:22:02,197
Mai, prosím, neboj sa....

239
00:22:03,114 --> 00:22:07,702
sveta, ktorý si si tak želala.

